snippet.title: Baptiste - Official Announcement Trailer | Steam | PS5
snippet.description:
🔗 Add it to your Steam wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2922250/Baptiste/

🔗 Add it to your PlayStation 5 wishlist: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10013181

Step into the depths of psychological horror with Baptiste, a game where fear doesn't just lurk in the shadows… it lives within you. Explore a world shrouded in mystery, solve unsettling puzzles, and uncover a dark story filled with disturbing secrets.

🕯️ Do you dare to face the terror?

🌑 Follow us for updates:

Twitter/X: https://x.com/firenutgames
Bluesky: https://web-cdn.bsky.app/profile/firenutgames.bsky.social
Discord: https://discord.gg/EWc6t3Yw
Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell 🔔 to stay tuned for more.

#BaptisteGame #HorrorGame #IndieHorror #PsychologicalHorror
